OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FSocial housing tenants were left in
OL,8,F"hazardous conditions" by Cardiff and
OL,9,FFlintshire Councils, with serious risk
OL,10,Fto health and damage to property, the
OL,11,Fhousing watchdog has found.
OL,13,FA report from the Public Services
OL,14,FOmbudsman found Cardiff Council failed
OL,15,Fto investigate a "significant" leak
OL,16,Fand "extensive" damp and mould over a
OL,17,Ffour-year period, leaving the property
OL,18,F"not fit for human habitation."
