OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FA second report from the watchdog
OL,8,Fdetailed failings by Flintshire
OL,9,FCouncil to respond to repeated reports
OL,10,Fof damp and mould over five months,
OL,11,Fposing a "significant" health hazard
OL,12,Fto the tenant and resulting in the
OL,13,Fchildren "suffering recurrent chest
OL,14,Finfections." All family members were
OL,15,Fforced to move out.
