OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FMichelle Morris, Public Services
OL,8,FOmbudsman for Wales, said: "A home
OL,9,Fshould be a place of peace and safety
OL,10,F- but for the people who brought these
OL,11,Fcomplaints to us, it became a hazard.
OL,12,FThe health impacts of damp and mould
OL,13,Fare well-documented, but its impact on
OL,14,Ffamily life can be no less
OL,15,Fdevastating."
OL,17,FCardiff Council report
