OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FIn this report, a tenant named Ms C
OL,8,Fcomplained the Council had not
OL,9,Fresponded to multiple reports of leaks
OL,10,Fand "extensive" damp and mould at the
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FShe added that after the property was
OL,14,Fdeemed "not fit for habitation," the
OL,15,Fcouncil failed to carry out repair
OL,16,Fworks in a "timely manner" or provide
OL,17,Fany alternative accommodation.
