OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FIn investigating Ms C's complaints,
OL,8,Fthe watchdog found the Council was
OL,9,Faware of damp and mould from April
OL,10,F2021. It found Ms C had made several
OL,11,Freports of a "significant" leak from
OL,12,Fthe bathroom that was causing damage
OL,13,Fto the kitchen ceiling, and that by
OL,14,FMarch 2024 the property had fallen
OL,15,Finto an "appalling state of disrepair."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/16
