OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FThe Ombudsman also found that there
OL,8,Fwere "further avoidable delays" in
OL,9,Farranging repairs after the Council
OL,10,Fformally decided that the property was
OL,11,F"not fit for human habitation" in July
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FIt noted that Ms C, her two daughters,
OL,15,Fand elderly mother spent "many months"
OL,16,Fliving in "unsuitable conditions"
OL,17,Fwithout access to a "home which was
OL,18,Ffit for them to live in."
