OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FOn the report, Morris said: "The
OL,8,Fservice failures uncovered in our
OL,9,Finvestigation had a devastating impact
OL,10,Fon Ms C and her family. The damp and
OL,11,Fmould posed significant hazards to the
OL,12,Fhealth of Ms C and her family, and
OL,13,Fdamaged or destroyed many of the
OL,14,Ffamily's possessions."
OL,16,F"The despair of living in such poor
OL,17,Fconditions over a long period appeared
OL,18,Fto have contributed to the slow
OL,19,Fdisintegration of the family unit to
OL,20,Fthe point that all family members had
OL,21,Fmoved out."
