OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FAs a result, the watchdog made a
OL,8,Fnumber of recommendations, all of
OL,9,Fwhich the Council accepted. These
OL,10,Fincluded providing a #3,000 in
OL,11,Ffinancial redress and apologising to
OL,12,FMs C.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the Ombudsman asked the
OL,15,FCouncil to provide all evidence review
OL,16,Foutcomes and action plans, as well as
OL,17,Fidentify any other tenants affected by
OL,18,Fsystematic issues and provide redress
OL,19,Fwhere needed.
