OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FIn a statement Cardiff Council said:
OL,8,F"The service provided to the contract
OL,9,Fholder was poor and fell well below
OL,10,Fthe standards we expect. We apologise
OL,11,Funreservedly for this, and for the
OL,12,Fimpact it had on her and her family.
OL,14,F"We take the Ombudsman's findings
OL,15,Fextremely seriously. Over the past
OL,16,Fyear, we have undertaken a
OL,17,Fcomprehensive review of the repairs
OL,18,Fservice and developed a wide-ranging
OL,19,Fimprovement plan to address both
OL,20,Fimmediate and systemic issues.
