OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,F"Considerable improvements have
OL,8,Falready been made, including reducing
OL,9,Foutstanding repairs, improving
OL,10,Fscheduling and workforce management,
OL,11,Fenhancing our response to damp and
OL,12,Fmould, and strengthening customer
OL,13,Fcommunication. While much progress has
OL,14,Fbeen made, we recognise there is more
OL,15,Fthat can be done and we are continuing
OL,16,Fwith our improvement programme."
OL,18,FFlintshire Council report
