OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FIn this report, a tenant named Miss Y
OL,8,Fcomplained about the way her landlord,
OL,9,FFlintshire County Council, responded
OL,10,Fto reports of damp and mould in her
OL,11,Fhome.
OL,13,FThe report found that the Council
OL,14,Ffailed to identify that Miss Y had
OL,15,Fmade numerous repair requests
OL,16,Fregarding the same issue, and added
OL,17,Fthat officers did visit Miss Y's home
OL,18,Fon several occasions to address new
OL,19,Fissues, while previous repairs were
OL,20,Fleft unattended.
