OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FAs a result, there were many missed
OL,8,Fopportunities to address the issues of
OL,9,Fdamp and mould.
OL,11,FIt also found the Council did not "act
OL,12,Fin a timely manner" once the full
OL,13,Fextent of the works needed was
OL,14,Fidentified. Therefore, Miss Y and her
OL,15,Fchildren were left living in
OL,16,F"unacceptable conditions" for five
OL,17,Fmonths.
