OL,3,CWelsh councils under fire for 'serious
OL,4,Cfailing' in resolving housing
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FOn the report, Morris said: "The
OL,8,Ffailings identified in this
OL,9,Finvestigation are significant. The
OL,10,FCouncil missed opportunities to
OL,11,Fidentify damp in Miss Y's home sooner.
OL,12,FWhen it became aware that extensive
OL,13,Fwork in relation to damp was needed,
OL,14,Fit did not take timely action to
OL,15,Fsecure alternative accommodation."
OL,17,F"As a result, Miss Y and her children
OL,18,Fwere left living in a home that the
OL,19,FCouncil knew to be severely impacted
OL,20,Fby damp during some of the coldest
OL,21,Fmonths of the year.
