OL,7,F"Miss Y said that living in a home
OL,8,Fwith damp and mould had led to both
OL,9,Fherself and her children suffering
OL,10,Frecurrent chest infections and that
OL,11,Fher youngest child had been diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith asthma. Due to them becoming
OL,13,Fdamaged by mould, Miss Y said that she
OL,14,Fhad to dispose of furniture, clothing
OL,15,Fand other possessions."
