OL,7,FIn a statement, Vicky Clark, Chief
OL,8,Fofficer for Housing and Communities
OL,9,Ffor Flintshire Council, said: "We
OL,10,Facknowledge the findings of the
OL,11,FOmbudsman report and accept that, on
OL,12,Fthis occasion, our response fell short
OL,13,Fof the standards we set and expect."
OL,15,F"We sincerely apologise to the tenant
OL,16,Ffor any stress and inconvenience
OL,17,Fcaused. Since this case, we have made
OL,18,Fchanges to how we respond to reports
OL,19,Fof damp and mould."
