OL,7,F"We now have processes in place to
OL,8,Factively monitor all reports to ensure
OL,9,Fany concerns are dealt with
OL,10,Fefficiently and effectively. Providing
OL,11,Fall tenants with safe, well-maintained
OL,12,Fhomes is a key priority for the
OL,13,FCouncil and we are determined to
OL,14,Fensure delivery of this high priority."
